Do not allow contradictory clues (e.g., can't clue a blue card as yellow)

change minsdk version to 15 to support 98% of devices

fix orientation to landscape for all activities

Fix bug preventing display of Negative info on lower resolution screens

Finalize changes for 1) Clue None of a Type, 2) Background color, 3) remember multistagetogglebuttons
